<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Jun 2022 06:03:34 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>傳 15 吋 MacBook 將有 M2 Pro 版，郭明錤：預計 2023 第二季推出</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/16/15inch-macbook-m2/notebook/mac-os/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=15inch-macbook-m2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Natalie]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jun 2022 06:03:34 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Mac]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple M2]]></category><category><![CDATA[macbook]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1104998</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>知名爆料人、天風國際分析師郭明錤日前指出，Apple 15 吋 MacBook 將會提供 M2 以及 M2 P [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">知名爆料人、天風國際分析師郭明錤日前指出，Apple 15 吋 MacBook 將會提供 M2 以及 M2 Pro 2 款晶片可搭配，預計會在 2023 年的上半年生產，最早會在明年第二季推出市場。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/vpavic_4291_20201113_0366.0.0-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/vpavic_4291_20201113_0366.0.0-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/vpavic_4291_20201113_0366.0.0-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/vpavic_4291_20201113_0366.0.0.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">郭明錤近日在 Twitter 發文更正他在 3 月作出的推測，指出 15 吋 MacBook</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;"> 將會在 2023 年上半年生產，搭配 35W 及 67W 的充電火牛，而不是他在 3 月預計的在 2023 年第四季生產、配以 30W 的火牛。但他並沒有對其 「新 15 吋 MacBook 不是命名為 MacBook Air」的揣測作任何回應。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Prediction updates:<br />1. New 15&quot; MacBook would go to mass production in mid-1H23, and launch date may be 2Q23 or later.<br />2. New 15&quot; MacBook may offer two CPU options, M2 (with 35W adapter) &amp; M2 Pro (with 67W adapter).<br />3. I haven&#39;t heard of any plans for rumored 12&quot; MacBook yet. <a href="https://t.co/zm09nMvG7R">https://t.co/zm09nMvG7R</a></p><p>&mdash; 郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo) (@mingchikuo) <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1537087795009044480?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 15, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">除此以外，郭明錤更預測出新 15 吋 MacBook 搭配 M2 及 M2 Pro 晶片在 CPU 配備的分別：M2 晶片版將會配上 35W Type-C 火牛，而 M2 Pro 晶片版將會配備 67W 的 Type-C 火牛。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而早前亦有消息指，12 吋 MacBook 將會在 2023 年底或 2024 年頭推出，但郭明錤指，他未有收到任個有關 12 吋 MacBook 的消息。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/06/15/kuo-15-inch-m2-macbook-2023-rumor/">Mac Rumors</a></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
